  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Assist in sales and promotional activities</p>\n<p>· Display and Replenish stock</p>\n<p>· Perform housekeeping duties</p>\n<p>· Good customer service skills, inquire about their needs and offer assistance</p>\n<p>· Attend to walk-in customers and build a good customer experience</p>\n<p>· Cashiering duties.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Preferably candidates with retail experience</p>\n<p>· Positive work attitude and cheerful personality</p>\n<p>· 5/6 day work week (including weekends &amp; public holidays)</p>\n<p>· Basic Knowledge in using computer/excel</p>\n<p>· Training will be provided.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants please forward your resume/CV with photo including expected salary and notice period to:<br>\nshiying<a href=\"mailto:hr@selffix.com\">@selffix.com</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Secondary education &amp; below</p>\n<p>- $8-10/hr (Part Timer)</p>\n<p>- Retail Assistant ($1600 / $1800)</p>\n<p>- Retail Executive ($1801-$2000)</p>",
